Package: miningKPI
Title: Mining Operations and Reliability Analytics
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Rafael", "da Silva Fernandes", , "rafasfer2@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides datasets and functions for calculating Key Performance Indicators (KPIs) in the mining industry. Includes tools for Overall Equipment Effectiveness (OEE), Reliability Engineering (MTBF, MTTR), and Asset Management. Contains anonymized real-world datasets from Iron Ore and Copper operations (Mina A, B, C, and D).
